00379 /**
00380  * cvmx_ase_backdoor_req_ctl
00381  *
00382  * This register is used to configure and trigger backdoor requests. Backdoor requests
00383  * can be inserted at any time. They are inserted into the request stream from LAP. The
00384  * request packet needs to be written to ASE_BACKDOOR_REQ_DATA(), and must be written
00385  * before [VALID] is triggered. Both [CNT] and [VALID] can be written in the same
